uui.qpic.cn/vcover_hz_pic/0/mzc00200eg087d01734502863428/0","vod_pic_slide":"https://vcover-hz-pic.puui.qpic.cn/vcover_hz_pic/0/mzc00200eg087d01734502863428/0","vod_pic_screenshot":"","vod_actor":"成龙,拉尔夫·马基奥,温明娜,乔舒亚·杰克逊,阿拉米斯·奈特","vod_director":"","vod_writer":"","vod_behind":"","vod_blurb":"功夫神童李峰（王班 饰）初到纽约，面临全新挑战，他决定登上比武赛场。他能否在中国传统武术大师韩（成龙 饰）与初代“功夫小子”丹尼尔（拉尔夫·马基奥 饰）的教导下，找到属于自己的武学之道？","vod_remarks":"完结","vod_pubdate":"2025","vod_total":0,"vod_serial":"1","vod_tv":"","vod_weekday":"","vod_area":"美国","vod_lang":"英语","vod_year":"2025","vod_version":"高清版","vod_state":"正片","vod_author":"","vod_jumpurl":"","vod_tpl":"","vod_tpl_play":"","vod_tpl_down":"","vod_isend":1,"vod_lock":0,"vod_level":7,"vod_copyright":0,"vod_points":0,"vod_points_play":0,"vod_points_down":0,"vod_hits":118,"vod_hits_day":1,"vod_hits_week":3,"vod_hits_month":1,"vod_duration":"","vod_up":1275,"vod_down":1099,"vod_score":"10.0","vod_score_all":1810,"vod_score_num":181,"vod_time":"2026-02-10 02:18:30","vod_time_add":"2025-09-15 12:45:15","vod_trysee":0,"vod_douban_id":0,"vod_douban_score":"0.0","vod_reurl":"","vod_rel_vod":"","vod_rel_art":"","vod_pwd":"","vod_pwd_url":"","vod_pwd_play":"","vod_pwd_play_url":"","vod_pwd_down":"","vod_pwd_down_url":"","vod_content":"<p>少年李峰初到纽约遭遇当地空手道高手挑衅霸凌，在积攒的怒火之下他决定绝地反击。为帮助李峰，昔日恩师韩师父找到空手道大师丹尼尔·拉鲁索共同对其进行武术指导。李峰以中国功夫为基础，不断吸收空手道技法，最终将两个流派融会贯通，开辟了属于自己的武学之道，并准备迎接一场惊心动魄的武术对决。</p>","vod_plot":0,"vod_plot_name":"","vod_plot_detail":"","type":{"type_id":21,"type_name":"电影","type_en":"dongzuopian","type_sort":999,"type_mid":1,"type_pid":20,"type_status":1,"type_tpl":"type.html","type_tpl_list":"show.html","type_tpl_detail":"detail.html","type_tpl_play":"","type_tpl_down":"","type_key":"","type_des":"","type_title":"","type_union":"","type_extend":{"class":"喜剧,爱情,动作,科幻,战争,谍战,警匪,犯罪,动画,奇幻,剧情,玄幻,戏曲,记录,武侠,冒险,枪战,恐怖,悬疑,传记,惊悚,经典,青春,文艺,微电影,古装,历史,运动,农村,儿童","area":"大陆,香港,台湾,美国,法国,英国,日本,韩国,德国,泰国,印度,意大利,西班牙,加拿大","lang":"","year":"2025,2024,2023,2022,2021,2020,2019,2018,2017,2016,2015,2014,