阳","vod_writer":"","vod_behind":"","vod_blurb":"陷入人生低谷的小说家路空文（董子健 饰）被巨大的诱惑牵引，导致他自己和书中的角色都陷入了不可逆转的危机。最终小说家找回了信念，与书中人一起拯救了双世界危机。","vod_remarks":"HD","vod_pubdate":"2025-10-01(中国大陆)","vod_total":1,"vod_serial":"1","vod_tv":"","vod_weekday":"","vod_area":"中国大陆","vod_lang":"汉语普通话","vod_year":"2025","vod_version":"","vod_state":"","vod_author":"","vod_jumpurl":"","vod_tpl":"","vod_tpl_play":"","vod_tpl_down":"","vod_isend":1,"vod_lock":0,"vod_level":7,"vod_copyright":0,"vod_points":0,"vod_points_play":0,"vod_points_down":0,"vod_hits":27097,"vod_hits_day":1,"vod_hits_week":2,"vod_hits_month":13,"vod_duration":"134分钟","vod_up":1112,"vod_down":1054,"vod_score":"6.5","vod_score_all":540,"vod_score_num":135,"vod_time":"2026-02-10 02:07:35","vod_time_add":"2025-10-02 16:10:03","vod_trysee":0,"vod_douban_id":35382381,"vod_douban_score":"6.5","vod_reurl":"","vod_rel_vod":"","vod_rel_art":"","vod_pwd":"","vod_pwd_url":"","vod_pwd_play":"","vod_pwd_play_url":"","vod_pwd_down":"","vod_pwd_down_url":"","vod_content":"<p>陷入人生低谷的小说家路空文（董子健 饰）被巨大的诱惑牵引，导致他自己和书中的角色都陷入了不可逆转的危机。最终小说家找回了信念，与书中人一起拯救了双世界危机。</p>","vod_plot":0,"vod_plot_name":"","vod_plot_detail":"","type":{"type_id":21,"type_name":"电影","type_en":"dongzuopian","type_sort":999,"type_mid":1,"type_pid":20,"type_status":1,"type_tpl":"type.html","type_tpl_list":"show.html","type_tpl_detail":"detail.html","type_tpl_play":"","type_tpl_down":"","type_key":"","type_des":"","type_title":"","type_union":"","type_extend":{"class":"喜剧,爱情,动作,科幻,战争,谍战,警匪,犯罪,动画,奇幻,剧情,玄幻,戏曲,记录,武侠,冒险,枪战,恐怖,悬疑,传记,惊悚,经典,青春,文艺,微电影,古装,历史,运动,农村,儿童","area":"大陆,香港,台湾,美国,法国,英国,日本,韩国,德国,泰国,印度,意大利,西班牙,加拿大","lang":"","year":"2025,2024,2023,2022,2021,2020,2019,2018,2017,2016,2015,2014,2013,2012,2011,2010","star":"","director":"","state":"","version":""},"type_logo":"","type_pic":"","type_jumpurl":"","type_1":{"type_id":20,"type_name":"电影","type_en":"dianying","type_sort":999,"type_mid":1,"type_pid":0,"type_status":1,"type_tpl":"type.html","type_tpl_list":"show.html","type_tp