枹罕镇正遭受强权恶霸的欺凌压迫，寒月刃决定出手相助，却惊觉人性中的软弱与恐惧远比暴力更加可怕……\r\n　　而他与曼陀罗（孙艺燃 饰）的纠缠如毒刃绞心，在心动与背叛间撕裂挣扎。\r\n　　当强权无德，弱者无公，必将有一把刀，劈开跪着的时代。","vod_remarks":"正片","vod_pubdate":"2025","vod_total":1,"vod_serial":"0","vod_tv":"","vod_weekday":"","vod_area":"内地","vod_lang":"国语","vod_year":"2025","vod_version":"高清版","vod_state":"正片","vod_author":"","vod_jumpurl":"","vod_tpl":"","vod_tpl_play":"","vod_tpl_down":"","vod_isend":1,"vod_lock":0,"vod_level":7,"vod_copyright":0,"vod_points":0,"vod_points_play":0,"vod_points_down":0,"vod_hits":52,"vod_hits_day":1,"vod_hits_week":1,"vod_hits_month":6,"vod_duration":"","vod_up":1432,"vod_down":1274,"vod_score":"0.0","vod_score_all":0,"vod_score_num":0,"vod_time":"2026-02-10 01:30:54","vod_time_add":"2025-10-10 11:45:07","vod_trysee":0,"vod_douban_id":0,"vod_douban_score":"0.0","vod_reurl":"","vod_rel_vod":"","vod_rel_art":"","vod_pwd":"","vod_pwd_url":"","vod_pwd_play":"","vod_pwd_play_url":"","vod_pwd_down":"","vod_pwd_down_url":"","vod_content":"<p>影片讲述威震江湖的“冷血刀客”寒月刃（李炳渊 饰），因一饭之恩重返枹罕镇，而此时的枹罕镇正遭受强权恶霸的欺凌压迫，寒月刃决定出手相助，却惊觉人性中的软弱与恐惧远比暴力更加可怕……\r\n　　而他与曼陀罗（孙艺燃 饰）的纠缠如毒刃绞心，在心动与背叛间撕裂挣扎。\r\n　　当强权无德，弱者无公，必将有一把刀，劈开跪着的时代。</p>","vod_plot":0,"vod_plot_name":"","vod_plot_detail":"","type":{"type_id":21,"type_name":"电影","type_en":"dongzuopian","type_sort":999,"type_mid":1,"type_pid":20,"type_status":1,"type_tpl":"type.html","type_tpl_list":"show.html","type_tpl_detail":"detail.html","type_tpl_play":"","type_tpl_down":"","type_key":"","type_des":"","type_title":"","type_union":"","type_extend":{"class":"喜剧,爱情,动作,科幻,战争,谍战,警匪,犯罪,动画,奇幻,剧情,玄幻,戏曲,记录,武侠,冒险,枪战,恐怖,悬疑,传记,惊悚,经典,青春,文艺,微电影,古装,历史,运动,农村,儿童","area":"大陆,香港,台湾,美国,法国,英国,日本,韩国,德国,泰国,印度,意大利,西班牙,加拿大","lang":"","year":"2025,2024,2023,2022,2021,2020,2019,2018,2017,2016,2015,2014,2013,2012,2011,2010","star":"","director":"","state":"","version":""},"type_logo":"","type_pic":"","type_jumpurl":"","type_1":{"type_id":20,"type_name":"电影","type_en":"dianying","type_sort":999,"type_mid":1,"type_pid":0,"type_status":1,"type_tpl":"ty