:"","vod_jumpurl":"","vod_tpl":"","vod_tpl_play":"","vod_tpl_down":"","vod_isend":1,"vod_lock":0,"vod_level":7,"vod_copyright":0,"vod_points":0,"vod_points_play":0,"vod_points_down":0,"vod_hits":29279,"vod_hits_day":2,"vod_hits_week":2,"vod_hits_month":12,"vod_duration":"","vod_up":1423,"vod_down":1392,"vod_score":"0.0","vod_score_all":0,"vod_score_num":0,"vod_time":"2026-02-09 23:36:19","vod_time_add":"2025-09-06 22:04:04","vod_trysee":0,"vod_douban_id":0,"vod_douban_score":"0.0","vod_reurl":"","vod_rel_vod":"","vod_rel_art":"","vod_pwd":"","vod_pwd_url":"","vod_pwd_play":"","vod_pwd_play_url":"","vod_pwd_down":"","vod_pwd_down_url":"","vod_content":"<p>　　平凡少年韩立出生贫困，为了让家人过上更好的生活，自愿前去七玄门参加入门考核，最终被墨大夫收入门下。<br/>　　墨大夫一开始对韩立悉心培养、传授医术，让韩立对他非常感激，但随着一同入门的弟子张铁失踪，韩立才发现了墨大夫的真面目。<br/>　　墨大夫试图夺舍韩立，最终却被韩立反杀。通过墨大夫的遗书韩立得知了一个全新世界：修仙界的存在。<br/>　　在帮助七玄门抵御外敌之后，韩立离开了七玄门，前去墨大夫的家中寻找暖阳宝玉解毒，并帮助墨家人打败了敌人。<br/>　　通过墨大夫之女墨彩环的口中得知太南小会地址，韩立为追寻修仙人的足迹决定前往太南小会，拜别家人后……</p>","vod_plot":0,"vod_plot_name":"","vod_plot_detail":"","type":{"type_id":44,"type_name":"动漫2","type_en":"dongman","type_sort":2,"type_mid":1,"type_pid":43,"type_status":1,"type_tpl":"type.html","type_tpl_list":"show.html","type_tpl_detail":"detail.html","type_tpl_play":"","type_tpl_down":"","type_key":"","type_des":"","type_title":"","type_union":"","type_extend":{"class":"喜剧,爱情,动作,科幻,战争,谍战,警匪,犯罪,动画,奇幻,剧情,玄幻,情色,家庭,伦理,戏曲,记录,西部,脱口秀,歌舞,音乐,魔幻,武侠,冒险,枪战,恐怖,悬疑,传记,惊悚,经典,青春,文艺","area":"大陆,香港,台湾,美国,法国,英国,日本,韩国,德国,泰国,印度,意大利,西班牙,加拿大","lang":"","year":"2025,2024,2023,2022,2021,2020,2019,2018,2017,2016,2015,2014,2013,2012,2011,2010","star":"","director":"","state":"","version":""},"type_logo":"","type_pic":"","type_jumpurl":"","type_1":{"type_id":43,"type_name":"动漫","type_en":"dongman","type_sort":2,"type_mid":1,"type_pid":0,"type_status":1,"type_tpl":"type.html","type_tpl_list":"show.html","type_tpl_detail":"detail.html","type_tpl_play":"","type_tpl_down":"","type_key":"","type_des":"","type_title":"","type_union":"","type_extend":{"class":"喜剧,爱情,